# Company Data & Research Standards

Full detail: `.playbook/11_COMPANY_SCHEMA.md`, `.playbook/07_RESEARCH_GUIDE.md`.

- Evidence over assumption. Every factual claim needs a traceable source (company's own careers page/case study >
  vendor-confirmed > reputable secondary > inference, in that priority order).
- `usesAEM: true` requires at least one entry in `Evidence`. If no source is found, set `Status: "Unverified"`
  instead of asserting it unsupported.
- Set `LastVerified` whenever evidence is checked.
- The `md/deep-research-report*.md` files are Tier 3/4 quality (hedged language, not cross-checked) — never copy
  them directly into `data/companies.json` as confirmed fact without applying the verification workflow first.
- No duplicate company entries across sources without reconciling conflicting details (priority scores, India
  presence, etc.) into one record.
